weeks.title: [CS2 V6] Agentsix1's Simple Bomb Timer
weeks.author: Agentsix1 : 316884
items: Shows when the bomb is being planted
Shows when the bomb is planted
Shows the damage the bomb will do to you
Shows the amount of time left on defuse
Defuse will turn red if unable to defuse
